        {
            "id": 6009069,
            "title": "陸媒：川普與習近平通話 白宮未回應",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據中國官媒《新華社》周四 (5 日) 報導，美國總統川普與中國國家主席習近平進行了電話通話。截稿前，白宮尚未對此消息立即回覆置評請求。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009069%2Fl%2F86eea1fba4bdec51e6db48080fa46066.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">陸媒：川普與習近平通話 白宮未回應(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新...</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
