            "id": 6009066,
            "title": "涉侵權案 大立光：已確認可繼續先前使用合法購買的軟體不被干擾",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光學元件股王大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日指出，大立光涉及軟體侵權爭議案件仍在審理中，並不影響營運，且大立光發布重大訊息指出，公司目前生產營運正常，對財務及業務並未受影響。公司並已確認可繼續使用合法購買的軟體不被干擾。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009066%2Fl%2F451210faaa4453078d2e68a0ca7b0e3d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">大立光涉侵權案 公司：已確認可繼續使用先前合法購買的軟體不被干擾。(鉅亨網記者張欽發攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大立光指出，德商發律師函要求大立光停止使用合法購買的軟體，為維護權益，大立光於是向法院就合法購買軟體的部份聲請定暫時狀態處分，禁止德商繼續騷擾。法院也認定德商對於大立光繼續使用合法購買的軟體並無意見，裁定無保全必要因而駁回大立光的聲請。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大立光指出，德商當庭向法官表示，對大立光先前合法購買的軟體「當然可以獲得授權使用」，法院也認定德商對於大立光繼續使用合法購買的軟體「並無意見」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大立光今天指出，大立光因主張合法使用已授權的軟體且德商也沒有意見是假處分案被駁回的原因，駁回後大立光確認可合法使用已授權的軟體，且已著手逐步汰換掉此一軟體在製程上的使用。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此一事件主要爲德商 Mvtec 在明 (6) 日大立光股東會前發出訊息指出，大立光去年因涉嫌盜用德商的影像檢測軟體被檢察官起訴，大立光董事長林恩平當時宣稱已開始汰換該軟體不再使用；不料德商兩度去函要求限期提出合法使用的授權證明，大立光拒不提供且向智慧財產法院聲請假處分，要求德商在侵權官司判決確定前「應容忍且不得以任何方式妨礙干擾大立光使用該軟體」，日前遭裁定駁回大立光的聲請。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6009066",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 21:03:49",
